➜火星伴月、流星雨、海王星冲日……9月精彩天象都在这里了→
http://www.sohu.com/a/415911053_114960	15840
<p><strong><span>（央视财经《正点财经》）</span></strong><span>根据天文预报显示，在</span><span>9</span><span>月，</span><span>“</span><span>火星伴月</span><span>”</span><span>、</span><span>“</span><span>英仙座艾普西隆流星雨极大</span><span>”</span><span>、</span><span>“</span><span>海王星冲日</span><span>”</span><span>等精彩天象将轮番上演。</span><span></span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="305" src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200901/f16850a72e214d79b1119327268cf01e.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>9</span><span>月，火星升起的时间已经提前到每天</span><span>20</span><span>点左右，亮度也进一步增加，观测条件较好。</span><span>9</span><span>月</span><span>6</span><span>日晚上，可以看到火星和明月一同升起，组成火星伴月的美丽天象，它们之间角距离大约只有</span><span>4</span><span>度，火星的亮度大约为负</span><span>2</span><span>等，在夜空中非常醒目。</span><span></span></p>
<p><img width="553" height="278" src="//p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200901/2448117bd4cc424981a27d09318aebf5.jpeg" /></p>
<p><img width="554" height="280" src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200901/75a32019ecbc4af7808da990e9064489.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
